                            <comment id="16049428" author="jwagenleitner" created="Wed, 14 Jun 2017 17:49:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Are you seeing this issue with 2.4.x?  I think the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/4ea1207f21b93a15dbcca17538c379721d9217de&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;commit 4ea1207f&lt;/a&gt; that introduced the call to &lt;tt&gt;InvokerHelper&lt;/tt&gt; was only added to 2.5+ and I don&apos;t see the code in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/blob/GROOVY_2_4_X/src/main/groovy/lang/GroovyClassLoader.java#L970&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;2.4 branch&lt;/a&gt;.  Just want to make sure on what version is affected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16049439" author="jbredeson" created="Wed, 14 Jun 2017 17:57:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry you are correct we are running a modified code base. We are running 2.4.10 with the addition of pull request &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/pull/445&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/groovy/pull/445&lt;/a&gt; to fix a memory leak we were having. That would make this a 2.5+ issue or an invalid issue depending on if the MetaClassRegistryImpl still works the same in 2.5+.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
